---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import TextTransformer from '@/components/TextTransformer';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Stylish Fonts Generator" 
  description="Generate multiple stylish font variations for your text with our free stylish fonts generator"
>
  <TextTransformer 
    client:load
    title="Stylish Fonts Generator" 
    description="Create beautiful, stylish text with multiple font variations" 
    transformType="stylish"
    placeholder="Enter your text to generate stylish fonts..."
  />

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">About Stylish Fonts Generator</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <p>The Stylish Fonts Generator creates multiple beautiful font variations of your text using Unicode characters. These stylish fonts work across most platforms and don't require any special software to display.</p>
          <p>Each font style has its own unique character and aesthetic, from elegant scripts to bold modern designs, giving you plenty of options to make your text stand out.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">How to Use</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Enter your text in the input field above</li>
            <li>Browse through the various stylish font options</li>
            <li>Click "Copy" next to any font style you like</li>
            <li>Paste your stylish text wherever you want to use it</li>
          </ol>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Font Styles Included</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Script:</strong> Elegant, flowing handwriting style</li>
            <li><strong>Bold Script:</strong> Thicker, more prominent script letters</li>
            <li><strong>Double-struck:</strong> Mathematical blackboard bold style</li>
            <li><strong>Bold Fraktur:</strong> Gothic, medieval-inspired letters</li>
            <li><strong>Sans-serif:</strong> Clean, modern without serifs</li>
            <li><strong>Small Caps:</strong> Compact capital letters</li>
            <li><strong>Squared:</strong> Letters enclosed in squares</li>
            <li><strong>Circled:</strong> Letters enclosed in circles</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-2">Perfect for</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Social media profiles and posts</li>
            <li>Website headers and titles</li>
            <li>Creative projects and designs</li>
            <li>Personal branding and logos</li>
            <li>Invitations and announcements</li>
            <li>Art and typography projects</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Note: These stylish fonts use Unicode characters that are supported by most modern devices and platforms. However, some older systems might not display all styles correctly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
